welcome to phlygh

Site rules:

1) Completly insulure search engine. Does not follow google seo rules. Not interested. S0rry.
2) Allows users to propose and vote on features given and taken away every month
3) enables users to display they're own ads, embed links on post
4) encourages users to maximize their content with unquie statictics made available
5) and interactive messaging system that substities as a fighting game or hangout
6) site wide chat: allowing everything to interact
7) Nothing is private except your password, beware
8) Have fun, post whatever, even offensive shit... no child pron though... you and your information will be reported to proper authorities immediatly. idiot.

How to use it?

welcome to "pop - top"

1) click fold buttons [start, learn, help, option])

brings up morphs

2) click (gui top_left [gear])

brings up nav top

3) click modal_nav_top_link_11

brings up menu right

4) click shortcut to perform site operations

Includes

Crud Post

messages & group messages

group & solo games

3) click modal_nav_top_link_4 (route

brings up page bottom 'aka a route page'
